title: Thank You Piratebay
description:
Dear Pirate Bay,

Over the years i have been a leech.  I have downloaded and not seeded, and haven&#039;t left comments.  This is wrong of me and I apologize.  You have helped me in my life countless times.  Thank you.  Thank you to the staff of Pirate Bay and thank you to the countless hosts who upload there projects for the rest of us.  You work hard for free and i am unable to praise you enough for your work.

If you find this, please know this isn&#039;t something written out of pure boredom but instead from the heart.  Please continue your projects and please credit the original creators.  With respect of others works, the community can become bigger and better then ever.

Thank you for all your hard work.

                                                        ~Sincerely Iball
